Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:18.91,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}有多少反叛者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.06,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}有多少梯子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:21.05,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}有多少叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.10,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}有多少猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.24,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}有多少槍枝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.27,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}被麻痺著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.34,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}你們害怕的不只是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:27.55,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}為人生乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.24,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}扣響扳機 開始暴動
